{
  "stem": "15393.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a house, and everybody gathered there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody came looking for someone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every day there was scenes, incredible scenes when somebody of the family found somebody of a family, they found each other.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It could have been the father, it could have been the cousin, it could have been the brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was incredible scenes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly one day, I learned that I was going to go to London.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't do anything in the direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I learnt I was going to London.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kahana-- this particular rabbi, Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Kahana, ?] who was by that time the chief rabbi of the Polish forces in Warsaw, put me on a list of children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Groups were being formed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a man by the name of Rabbi Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] here in London.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this man was a walking miracle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This man was something so remarkable, what achievements for him are-- I mean, so many that one cannot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But those who know who he was will know who I'm talking about.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he decided that he's going to bring out children from after-- aftermath of war from Poland, take them out of there and give them a chance in life.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so he brought out three transports of children after the war, not to mention the transport of children he brought before the war, but I'm not talking about that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But after the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was in touch with the Rabbi Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Kahana, ?] who was his go-between, if you like, on the other side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was a whole organization buying out children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "People didn't want to part with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Some people didn't want to give them back.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
